  m_text: "A galaxy is a gravitationally bound system of stars, gas, dust, and dark
    matter. There are an estimated 2 trillion\ngalaxies in the observable universe.
    Our home, the Milky Way, is a barred spiral galaxy containing 100\u2013400 billion\nstars
    and stretching roughly 100,000 light-years across. Galaxies come in four main
    shapes: spiral, elliptical,\nlenticular, and irregular. They cluster together
    in groups \u2014 our Local Group contains more than 54 galaxies,\ndominated by
    the Milky Way and Andromeda."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
